Package: handbrake-rk3588
Version: 1.0.0
Section: video
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: HandBrake RK3588 Team <rk3588@example.com>
Description: HandBrake GTK with RK3588 hardware acceleration
 HandBrake is a tool for converting video from nearly any format
 to a selection of modern, widely supported codecs.
 .
 This package includes GTK GUI (ghb) optimized for RK3588 platforms,
 with support for hardware encoding/decoding via Rockchip MPP and RGA.
Depends: libgtk-4-1, libglib2.0-0, libadwaita-1-0, libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0,
 libass9, libmp3lame0, libopus0, libspeex1, libvpx9,
 libbluray2, libdvdnav4, libdvdread8, libjansson4,
 libx264-164, libx265-199, libtheora0, libvorbis0a, libogg0,
 libturbojpeg0, libnuma1, libsvtav1enc0, libxml2,
 librga2, librockchip-mpp1, jellyfin-ffmpeg7
Homepage: https://handbrake.fr
